FT  26 APR 94 / Observer: Tall order
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Has cookery writer and restaurateur Prue Leith, who once took it upon
herself to uncurl the British Rail sandwich, bitten off more than she can
chew? For last night's annual dinner at the Institute of Chartered
