<HEADLINE>
FT  26 APR 94 / Engineers report small pay rises
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Annual pay settlements rose by an average of just 2.2 per cent at Yorkshire
and Humberside engineering companies during the first three months of this
year.
A tenth of settlements involved no increase at all, the region's Engineering
Employers' Association said yesterday.
