<HEADLINE>
FT  26 APR 94 / Inward investment in Wales reduced
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Fewer inward investment projects were won by Wales in 1993-94 than in the
previous year. The number fell from 201 to 169, and the capital expenditure
involved dropped from Pounds 950m to Pounds 765m.
