<HEADLINE>
FT  26 APR 94 / World News in Brief: Blast hits China's satellite launch
plans
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An explosion at China's space centre, which destroyed a Dollars 75m (Pounds
50m) advanced weather satellite, damaged the country's efforts to break into
the world commercial satellite launch market.
Page 6; Heavy brigade under assault, Page 21
</TEXT>
<XX>
