<HEADLINE>
FT  25 APR 94 / South African Elections: Voters, parties, personalities
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
VOTERS BY PROVINCE AND RACE
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
South Africa
