 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
African     81.4%          African     30.6%         African     18.4%
White       15.9%          White       19.1%         White       27.6%
Indian       0.1%          Indian       0.2%         Indian       0.9%
Coloured     2.6%          Coloured    50.0%         Coloured    53.0%
Voters      7.25m          Voters      0.44m         Voters      2.40m
Percentage of              Percentage of             Percentage of
total voting               total voting              total voting
population    7.2          population    1.9         population   10.6
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Eastern Cape               Natal                     North-West
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
African     83.2%          African     78.0%         African     88.0%
White        8.6%          White        9.7%         White       10.5%
Indian       0.3%          Indian      10.9%         Indian       0.3%
Coloured     7.8%          Coloured     1.4%         Coloured     1.2%
Voters      3.18m          Voters      4.59m         Voters      1.73m
Percentage of              Percentage of             Percentage of
total voting               total voting              total voting
